      "language": "Python",
      "code": "```python\nimport typing\nfrom configparser import ConfigParser\n\ndef get_config(section: str, option: str) -> typing.Optional[typing.Any]:\n    parser = ConfigParser()\n    parser.read('config.ini')\n    return parser.get(section, option)\n\ndef main():\n    config_value = get_config('database', 'host')\n    if config_value is not None:\n        print(f'Database host: {config_value}')\n\nif __name__ == "__main__":\n    main()\n```"
